		<title>欧洲时段前瞻：贸易谈判有望市场反弹；关注英国服务业PMI和美国贸易帐</title>
		<link>https://www.xmglobal.com/cn/markets-recover-on-hopes-for-trade-negotiations-uk-services-pmi-and-us-trade-data-due-67637</link>
